 📖 ABOUT THIS PROJECT
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

VPDLX is a fully class-based, virtual logging system for PowerShell. It allows
developers and system administrators to create, manage, and query multiple
in-memory log files simultaneously — without touching the filesystem — and
export them to disk in multiple formats (TXT, LOG, CSV, JSON) whenever needed.

Designed with clean OOP principles in mind, VPDLX provides both a low-level
class API ([Logfile], [FileDetails], [FileStorage]) and a high-level Public
Wrapper layer for everyday scripting use.

